<!DOCTYPE html>
<html dir="ltr" lang="en-US">
<head>
	{{>head}}
</head>

<body>
	{{>nav}}

	<div class="row">

		<div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-3" style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:48px">
			<h1>Landing Page</h1>
			<hr />
			<div class="grey-box">
				<h3>Purpose</h3>
				<hr />
				<p>
					This is the primary promotional page that visitors should see who are not registered users. The content should consist of feature descriptions and a prominent call-to-action for user registration.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="grey-box">
				<h3>User Registration</h3>
				<hr />
				<p>
					The following user registration form sends a POST request the the 'register' hander in the auth.js route found in the /routes directory. Upon successful registration, the site redirects to the 'dashboard.mustache' page.
				</p>

				<br />

				<form action="/auth/register" method="POST">
					<input class="form-control" type="text" name="email" placeholder="Email" /><br />
					<input class="form-control" type="text" name="username" placeholder="Username" /><br />
					<input class="form-control" type="password" name="password" placeholder="Password" /><br />
					<button type="submit" class="btn btn-info">Sign Up</button>
				</form>
			</div>

			<div class="grey-box">
				<h3>User Login</h3>
				<hr />
				<p>
					The following user login form sends a POST request the the 'login' hander in the auth.js route found in the /routes directory. Upon successful login, the site redirects to the 'dashboard.mustache' page.
				</p>

				<br />

				<form action="/auth/login" method="POST">
					<input class="form-control" type="text" name="email" placeholder="Email" /><br />
					<input class="form-control" type="password" name="password" placeholder="Password" /><br />
					<button type="submit" class="btn btn-info">Log In</button>
				</form>
			</div>			

		</div>
	</div>


  <!-- Turbo library imports: jQuery, Turbo CDN, sample app.js.
  NOTE: These should be minified in a build script -->
  <script type="text/javascript" src="/js/jquery.js"></script>

  <!-- For file uploading. Remove if file upload not necessry -->
  <script type="text/javascript" src="/js/dropzone.js"></script> 

  <!-- Turbo CDN. Better to use CDN than to store locally. -->
  <script type="text/javascript" src="https://cdn.turbo360-dev.com/dist/turbo.min.js"></script>

  <!-- Your app specific code -->
  <script type="text/javascript" src="/js/app.js"></script>
</body>
</html>